# -*- mode: conf; -*-

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User lunaryorn@gmail.com
PassCmd "imap-pass lunaryorn@gmail.com"
UseIMAPS yes
RequireSSL yes
UseTLSv1.2 yes

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Documents/Mail/
Inbox ~/Documents/Mail/Inbox
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Master :gmail:
Slave :local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]/* [Gmail]/Drafts "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred"
Create Slave
Expunge None
Sync All
